Subject: Secunia Research: CA ARCserve Backup RPC "handle_t" Argument Vulnerability

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 11/12/2008

     - CA ARCserve Backup RPC "handle_t" Argument Vulnerability -

====================================================================== 
